{"type":null,"faqId":10128,"title":"G6-U00如何启用屏幕解锁图案？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span>1.<span> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>安全</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>屏幕锁定</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>图案</b>。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>2.<span> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">在“<b>选择您的图案</b>”界面，通过手指在屏幕连续划过几个圆的圆心设定解锁时使用的图形样式，再点击“<b>继续</b>”。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>3.</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">再次在屏幕上划过刚才的样式，点击“<b>确认</b>”完成解锁图形的设置。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>4.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入图案解锁界面，在该界面划过刚才的图案样式，进行解锁。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:106.3pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30701\" /></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"707","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396602327000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":45,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"解锁","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}